ass=\"a\">兼职教师</a></li>\n           \n    <li><a href=\"../../rydw.htm#sz4\" class=\"a\">博士后</a></li>\n           \n    <li><a href=\"../../rydw.htm#sz5\" class=\"a\">行政人员</a></li>\n           \n    <li><a href=\"../../rydw.htm#sz6\" class=\"a\">实验员</a></li>\n           \n</ul>\n\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"fl1 n_pad1\">\n      <div class=\"wp flexjs\">\n        <div class=\"left\">\n          <div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\">_getBatchClickTimes('null',2110873241,'wbnews','u10')</script>\n<script>function seeContenta10(contentid,size,displayid){    document.getElementById(contentid).innerHTML = '[';    for(var i=0;i<=size;i++){        var allcontentid = contentid+(i+1);        if(allcontentid==displayid){            document.getElementById(contentid).innerHTML += \" <span id='\"+allcontentid+\"' name='\"+allcontentid+\"'  >\"+(i+1)+\"</span> \";            document.getElementById(displayid).style.display = 'block';        }else{            document.getElementById(contentid).innerHTML += \" <span style='cursor:pointer' id='\"+allcontentid+\"' name='\"+allcontentid+\"' onclick=seeContenta10('\"+contentid+\"','\"+size+\"','\"+allcontentid+\"')  >\"+(i+1)+\"</span> \";            document.getElementById(allcontentid).style.display = 'none';        }    }    document.getElementById(contentid).innerHTML += ']';}</script>\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/mp4video.js\"></script>\n<script>_addDynClicks('wbnews',2110873241,4117)</script>\n\n<div class=\"box box0 box1 flex\">\n            <div class=\"imgBox trans\">\n              <div class=\"img light\">\n                <img src=\"../../zpyx/houpanyu.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"con con1\">\n              <h3>侯攀宇</h3>\n              <h6></h6>\n              <p>助理教授</p>\n              <p>离子量子计算；金刚石色心量子信息应用。</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n    <div class=\"box box0 box2 aos-init aos-animate\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\n       \n         <h3 class=\"h3-5 flex\"></h3>\n                <div class=\"arc-con arc-cons1\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">My research interest focuses on the physical implementation of quantum information processing, specifically in the areas of quantum computing using trapped ions, as well as quantum simulation and quantum sensing using color centers in diamond.</p>\n</div></div>\n \n  </div>\n  \n    <div class=\"box box0 box3 aos-init aos-animate\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\n       \n         <h3 class=\"h3-5 flex\"><img src=\"../../images/h3-5.png\" alt=\"\">Education</h3>\n                <div class=\"arc-con arc-cons1\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">2013-2018 Ph.D. in Physics, Tsinghua University (supervisor: Prof. Lu-Ming Duan)</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">2009-2013 B.S. in Physics, Tsinghua University</p></div>\n \n  </div>\n  \n    <div class=\"box box0 box3 aos-init\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\n       \n         <h3 class=\"h3-5 flex\"><img src=\"../../images/h3-5.png\" alt=\"\">Employment</h3>\n                <div class=\"arc-con arc-cons1\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">2023-now Assistant Professor, IIIS, Tsinghua University</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">2018-2023 Postdoc, Ion Storage Group, NIST Boulder &amp; Univ. of Colorado Boulder</p></div>\n \n  </div>\n  \n    <div class=\"box box0 box3 aos-init\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\n       \n         <h3 class=\"h3-5 flex\"><img src=\"../../images/h3-5.png\" alt=\"\">Research activity</h3>\n                <div class=\"arc-con arc-cons1\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">Reviwer for Phys. Rev. Lett., PRX, PRX Quantum, Phys. Rev. A, , Phys. Rev. Applied, Annals of Physics, etc..</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">Guest editor in Frontier in Physics.</p></div>\n \n  </div>\n  \n    <div class=\"box box0 box3 aos-init\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\n       \n         <h3 class=\"h3-5 flex\"><img src=\"../../images/h3-5.png\" alt=\"\">Preprint</h3>\n                <div class=\"arc-con arc-cons1\"><p><span style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\">Y-Y Chen, K Li, L Zhang, Y-K Wu, J-Y Ma, H-X Yang, C Zhang, B-X Qi, Z-C Zhou, </span><b style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\">P-Y Hou#</b><span style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\">, Y Xu</span><b style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\">#</b><span style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\">, L-M Duan#, Quantum tomography of a third-order exceptional point in a dissipative trapped ion, arXiv:2412.05870</span></p></div>\n \n  </div>\n  \n    <div class=\"box box0 box3 aos-init\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\n       \n         <h3 class=\"h3-5 flex\"><img src=\"../../images/h3-5.png\" alt=\"\">Publication (∗ first author, # corresponding author)</h3>\n                <div class=\"arc-con arc-cons1\"><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\">27. Chenxi Wang, Chuanxin Huang, Hongxuan Zhang, Hongyuan Hu, Zhichao Mao, <b>Panyu Hou</b>, Yukai Wu, Zichao Zhou, Luming Duan, Experimental realization of direct entangling gates between dual-type qubits, Physical Review Letters 134 (1), 010601<br></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\">26. Jenny J Wu, <b>Pan-Yu Hou</b>, Stephen D Erickson, Adam D Brandt, Yong Wan, Giorgio Zarantonello, Daniel C Cole, Andrew C Wilson, Daniel H Slichter, Dietrich Leibfried. Electromagnetically-Induced-Transparency Cooling with a Tripod Structure in a Hyperfine Trapped Ion with Mixed-Species Crystals, PRA accepted (2025)</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\">25. Xiu-Ying Chang∗, <b>Pan-Yu Hou∗,</b><b>#</b>, Wen-Gang Zhang∗, Xiang-Qian Meng, Ye-Fei Yu, Ya-Nan Lu, Yan-Qing Liu, Bin-Xiang Qi, Dong-Ling Deng<b>#</b> and Lu-Ming Duan<b>#</b>. Hybrid entanglement and error correction in a scalable quantum network node, Nature Physics, 1-7 (2025)</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\">24. S.-A. Guo∗, Y.-K. Wu∗, J. Ye, L. Zhang, Y. Wang, W.-Q. Lian, R. Yao, Y.-L. Xu, C. Zhang, Y.-Z. Xu, B.-X. Qi, <b>P.-Y. Hou</b>, L. He, Z.-C. Zhou and L.-M. Duan. Hamiltonian learning for 3